    <item>
      <title>美国核心 CPI 涨幅与预期一致，为 0.3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-13/us-core-cpi-rises-in-line-with-estimates-at-0-3-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[10 月份，衡量美国基本通胀的指标保持坚挺，所谓的核心消费者价格指数（不包括食品和能源成本）连续第三个月上涨 0.3%，比去年同期上涨 3.3%。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台上对这些数字进行了分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-13/us-core-cpi-rises-in-line-with-estimates-at-0-3-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 13:56:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀与预期一致，交易员加大对美联储 12 月降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/traders-boost-bets-on-december-fed-cut-after-in-line-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商加大对美联储将在通胀数据符合预期后下个月将利率再次降低四分之一个百分点的押注，美国国债价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/traders-boost-bets-on-december-fed-cut-after-in-line-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 13:55:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
